article_id:223,category_name:News,title_name:A Gift of Gratitude for your Continued Support,image_path:,message:<div>We would like to extend our thanks to all the visitors of our Dragalia Lost booths at the Tokaigi 2019 and Taipei Game Show 2019 held last week-end.</div><div><br></div><div>As a token of our appreciation for your continued support, we will send out the following gift to players who started the game before <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1548658800"></span>:</div><div><br></div><div>Wyrmite x1500</div><div><br></div><div>For players who log in before <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1549263599"></span>, this gift can be claimed from your goodie box for up to 7 days after reception.</div><div><br></div><div>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.</div>,start_time:1548658800,update_time1548667254